      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNIGHT PHANTOM (1) steps out for the first time at this course. In the money last start when second (43.43) at The Meadows over 730m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances. EMERALD DOWNS (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (35.07) at Sandown behind Flying Discrete in a Restricted WIN. Has the pace to be prominent. Got the money at her only try from this box. Hard to beat again. LADY NESS (3) finds it hard to win but has a consistent overall record, having placed 13 of 25 career runs. Finished third (38.36) at Ballarat last time making it three minors on end. Can feature again. JULEA RUSLIE (7) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 0.9 lengths second (34.90) in a Restricted WIN at Sandown.",
